      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's what i'm afraid of. it's just that it feels so targeted lately. like, my smart bulb dimmed specifically right when i started getting a headache and felt really overwhelmed this afternoon. it's way too specific to be a coincidence. do u think they'd actually use individual homes to test these algorithms in real-time? like, using people as live subjects for their emotional tracking tech?",
