      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The difficulty in discerning the difference between \"smart\" automation and active emotional profiling is a key feature of the technology itself. Because the analysis happens within the background processing of the device, there is no obvious visual indicator that it is \"reading\" your mood. To protect yourself, you must approach these devices with the understanding that consent is often implicit in the terms of service. The most effective defense is to limit the data streams you allow into your home network, thereby starving the algorithms of the necessary emotional data to function.",
